**Job Position**: Sales Consultant

**Key Responsibilities:**
- Work within a high performing sales team.
- Sale in a residential construction environment.
- Understand new home market.

**Required Skills/Competencies:**
- 1+ years of experience in a similar sales role.
- Proven track record of sales in a residential construction environment.
- Strong background & understanding of the new home market.
- Excellent communication skills.
- Well-presented.

**Key Words/Phrases:**
- Sales Consultant
- Residential construction environment
- High performing sales team
- Communication skills
- Understand new home market.